ion: Limited for arginine.\n   - (2) Thermodynamic plausibility: Supported for general amino acid synthesis.\n   - (3) Theoretical proposal: Plausible but incomplete for arginine.\n\n---\n\n### Conclusion\nThe prebiotic synthesis of arginine remains an open question with significant gaps in experimental evidence and mechanistic detail. While general pathways for amino acid synthesis are well-supported, specific routes for arginine require further investigation, particularly in hydrothermal systems and guanidino group incorporation.\n=== END KNOWLEDGE BASE RESEARCH FINDINGS ===\n\n=== END LITERATURE RESEARCH ===\n\nConsider how well the network aligns with this literature in your evaluation.\n\n\nPlease evaluate the network and respond with JSON:\n{\n    \"pathway_evaluations\": [\n        {\n            \"pathway_id\": \"<id>\",\n            \"reaction_scores\": {\"rxn_001\": 0.85, ...},\n            \"chemical_feasibility\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"pathway_coherence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"environmental_progression\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"target_achievement\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"feedback\": \"<pathway-specific feedback>\",\n            \"approved\": <true if confidence >= 0.8>,\n            \"problematic_reactions\": [\"rxn_ids with issues\"],\n            \"suggestions\": [\"improvements\"]\n        }\n    ],\n    \"best_pathway_id\": \"<id of best pathway>\",\n    \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"network_feedback\": \"<overall assessment>\",\n    \"approved\": <true if any pathway approved>,\n    \"hub_quality\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"convergence_quality\": <0.0-1.0>\n}\n", "raw_response": "{\n  \"pathway_evaluations\": [\n    {\n      \"pathway_id\": \"P1\",\n      \"reaction_scores\": {\n        \"rxn_001\": 0.82,\n        \"rxn_002\": 0.62,\n        \"rxn_003\": 0.45,\n        \"rxn_005\": 0.28,\n        \"rxn_007\": 0.74,\n        \"rxn_010\": 0.55,\n        \"rxn_011\": 0.8,\n        \"r